Code:

class RemovePunctuation {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        
        String input = "Hello! World!";
        boolean bool = true;
        String ans = "";
        
        for(int i=0; i<input.length(); i++)
        {
            if(input.charAt(i) != '!')
            {
                ans = ans + input.charAt(i);
            }
            
        }
        
        System.out.println(ans);
        
    }
}

Output:
Hello World
